\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Style Design College is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer a Diploma in Graphic Design by the HEQC. Currently the institution has applied for the accreditation of the following programmes\'3A\line - Bachelor of Arts Degree in Photography\line - Bachelor of Arts Degree in Graphic Design \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
